struct.exostring: Matrik inits with the player as soon as they exit the room and the explosion effect has fired. At the end of this dialog have him escape area and destroy himself. If players try to open door after this it won't open and they get the message of "The stench of smoke assails your nostrils as you approach. The door, however, is blocked by rubble on the other side and will not open."
Script him to run out of the building. As soon as the player exits and the door shuts fire an explosion effect, lock the door and have Matrik init dialog.
